</figure>

<p>
This is a little similar to <a href="https://masto.ai/@jiewawa/110892569631167381">@jiewawa@masto.ai colouring pinyin based on tone in Org Mode</a>.
</p></li>

<li>I've been using <i>il faut</i> and <i>a besoin de</i> a bit more so that it's not all <i>dois</i> this and <i>dois</i> that.</li>
</ul>
